org.dockbox.selene.api.i18n.annotations

Annotation Type Resources


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface Resources
    The interface to indicate a type defines one or more resource(s). This is typically picked up by ResourceService to collect all known resources during init phases.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      java.lang.Class<?> value
      The module/type responsible for the resources.
